[2026-05-19T02:16:26.620Z] [STDOUT] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_pfho7zjo1qp1_1","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Task: 012-article-reader-02-design\n2\t\n3\t# Design: Article Reader\n4\t\n5\tGenerate the HTML design mockup for **Article Reader** using the **Flutter HTML Glossary** constrained vocabulary.\n6\t\n7\t## Critical Constraint\n8\t\n9\tThe HTML MUST use ONLY elements from the **Flutter HTML Glossary** (`stitch-flutter/references/flutter-html-glossary.md`). This ensures the `stitch-flutter` converter can produce pixel-perfect Flutter widgets mechanically.\n10\t\n11\t## Inputs\n12\t- `.stitch/designs/article-reader/SPEC.md` — Screen specification\n13\t- `.stitch/system/DESIGN.md` — Design system\n14\t- `.stitch/system/META.md` — Reference examples metadata\n15\t\n16\t## Steps\n17\t\n18\t1. **Read spec** — Load `.stitch/designs/article-reader/SPEC.md` to understand layout, sections, data\n19\t2. **Read glossary** — Load `stitch-flutter/references/flutter-html-glossary.md` to understand the constrained vocabulary\n20\t3. **Select best example match** — Read `.stitch/system/META.md` and score against examples per `stitch-generate/references/selecting-examples.md`\n21\t4. **Read matched reference** — Study the matching example's patterns\n22\t5. **Generate META.md** — Write `.stitch/designs/article-reader/META.md` with example selection and scoring table\n23\t6. **Generate design.html** — Write `.stitch/designs/article-reader/design.html` following `stitch-generate` skill using ONLY glossary elements\n24\t\n25\t## Glossary Quick Reference\n26\t\n27\t- Layout: `.column`, `.row`, `.stack`, `.wrap`, `.expanded`, `.padding`, `.sized-box`\n28\t- Scaffold: `.scaffold`, `.app-bar`, `.body`, `.bottom-nav`, `.fab`\n29\t- Text: `.title-large`, `.body-medium`, `.label-small` (Material 3 TextTheme classes)\n30\t- Components: `.card`, `.chip`, `.list-tile`, `.divider`, `.badge`, `.avatar`\n31\t- Buttons: `.elevated-btn`, `.filled-btn`, `.text-btn`, `.icon-btn`\n32\t- Images: `.network-image`, `.placeholder-image`\n33\t- Icons: `<svg class=\"icon\" data-name=\"{material_icon}\" data-size=\"24\">`\n34\t- Colors: `data-color=\"primary\"`, `data-bg=\"surface\"` (ColorScheme roles)\n35\t- Spacing: `data-spacing=\"md\"`, `data-p=\"lg\"` (token names)\n36\t- Animation: `data-animate=\"fade-in\"`, `data-animate-delay=\"100\"`\n37\t- Navigation: `.ink-well` with `data-route=\"/path\"`\n38\t\n39\t## Output\n40\t\n41\t- `.stitch/designs/article-reader/META.md` — Example selection and scoring\n42\t- `.stitch/designs/article-reader/design.html` — Self-contained HTML mockup at 375px using glossary vocabulary"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"92c85158-35a7-431a-be08-06a1045e3fef","uuid":"cac5b9fa-65a6-426a-9e31-c7283531895b","timestamp":"2026-05-19T02:16:26.619Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.converge/journal/default/tasks/012-article-reader-02-design/attempts/wip/TASK.md","content":"# Task: 012-article-reader-02-design\n\n# Design: Article Reader\n\nGenerate the HTML design mockup for **Article Reader** using the **Flutter HTML Glossary** constrained vocabulary.\n\n## Critical Constraint\n\nThe HTML MUST use ONLY elements from the **Flutter HTML Glossary** (`stitch-flutter/references/flutter-html-glossary.md`). This ensures the `stitch-flutter` converter can produce pixel-perfect Flutter widgets mechanically.\n\n## Inputs\n- `.stitch/designs/article-reader/SPEC.md` — Screen specification\n- `.stitch/system/DESIGN.md` — Design system\n- `.stitch/system/META.md` — Reference examples metadata\n\n## Steps\n\n1. **Read spec** — Load `.stitch/designs/article-reader/SPEC.md` to understand layout, sections, data\n2. **Read glossary** — Load `stitch-flutter/references/flutter-html-glossary.md` to understand the constrained vocabulary\n3. **Select best example match** — Read `.stitch/system/META.md` and score against examples per `stitch-generate/references/selecting-examples.md`\n4. **Read matched reference** — Study the matching example's patterns\n5. **Generate META.md** — Write `.stitch/designs/article-reader/META.md` with example selection and scoring table\n6. **Generate design.html** — Write `.stitch/designs/article-reader/design.html` following `stitch-generate` skill using ONLY glossary elements\n\n## Glossary Quick Reference\n\n- Layout: `.column`, `.row`, `.stack`, `.wrap`, `.expanded`, `.padding`, `.sized-box`\n- Scaffold: `.scaffold`, `.app-bar`, `.body`, `.bottom-nav`, `.fab`\n- Text: `.title-large`, `.body-medium`, `.label-small` (Material 3 TextTheme classes)\n- Components: `.card`, `.chip`, `.list-tile`, `.divider`, `.badge`, `.avatar`\n- Buttons: `.elevated-btn`, `.filled-btn`, `.text-btn`, `.icon-btn`\n- Images: `.network-image`, `.placeholder-image`\n- Icons: `<svg class=\"icon\" data-name=\"{material_icon}\" data-size=\"24\">`\n- Colors: `data-color=\"primary\"`, `data-bg=\"surface\"` (ColorScheme roles)\n- Spacing: `data-spacing=\"md\"`, `data-p=\"lg\"` (token names)\n- Animation: `data-animate=\"fade-in\"`, `data-animate-delay=\"100\"`\n- Navigation: `.ink-well` with `data-route=\"/path\"`\n\n## Output\n\n- `.stitch/designs/article-reader/META.md` — Example selection and scoring\n- `.stitch/designs/article-reader/design.html` — Self-contained HTML mockup at 375px using glossary vocabulary","numLines":42,"startLine":1,"totalLines":42}}}
