95	
96	- Hero display: 0pt (set solid)
97	- Screen titles: -0.5pt (slight tightening for large type)
98	- Body text: 0.15pt (open, readable spacing)
99	- Caption and labels: 0.4pt (clear separation for small text)
100	
101	---
102	
103	## 4. Component Styles
104	
105	### Card
106	- **Corner radius:** 16 points
107	- **Shadow depth:** Soft, diffused shadow — 8 points blur, 2 points offset-y, rgba(0,0,0,0.08) in light mode; rgba(0,0,0,0.25) in dark mode. The shadow feels like gentle morning light creating a soft pool beneath the card.
108	- **Background:** Morning Mist (#FAFAFA) in light mode; Deep Twilight (#1E1B2E) in dark mode
109	- **Internal padding:** 16 points all sides; 20 points for cards containing action buttons
110	- **Tap feedback:** Subtle scale-down to 98% on press, with 200ms ease-out return. The press feels like a gentle press into a soft surface rather than a click.
111	- **Spacing between cards:** 12 points
112	
113	### Buttons
114	
115	**Primary Button**
116	- Shape: Pill-shaped (fully rounded on all corners, corner radius equals half the button height)
117	- Minimum height: 48 points (touch target compliance)
118	- Background: Lavender Bloom (#7C3AED) in light mode; Twilight Bloom (#9F67FF) in dark mode
119	- Text: White (#FFFFFF), SemiBold, 14pt
120	- Press feedback: 200ms ease-out scale to 95%, background darkens by 8% brightness
121	- Corner radius: 24 points (fully rounded pill)
122	
123	**Secondary Button**
124	- Shape: Pill-shaped
125	- Minimum height: 48 points
126	- Background: Transparent with Lavender Bloom border (2 points stroke) in light mode; Transparent with Twilight Bloom border in dark mode
127	- Text: Lavender Bloom (#7C3AED) in light mode; Twilight Bloom (#9F67FF) in dark mode
128	- Press feedback: 200ms ease-out scale to 95%, background fills with 10% primary color
129	- Corner radius: 24 points
130	
131	**Text Button**
132	- Shape: No background, no border
133	- Minimum height: 48 points
134	- Text: Lavender Bloom (#7C3AED) in light mode; Text button inherits no background, only color
135	- Press feedback: 200ms ease-out opacity reduction to 60%
136	
137	**FAB (Floating Action Button)**
138	- Size: 56 points diameter
139	- Background: Lavender Bloom (#7C3AED); Twilight Bloom (#9F67FF) in dark mode
140	- Icon: White, 24 points
141	- Shadow: Medium diffused shadow, 12 points blur
142	- Press feedback: 200ms scale to 90%, shadow intensifies slightly
143	
144	### Text Input
145	- **Decoration style:** Filled background — a rounded container that feels like a gentle trough for text
146	- **Corner radius:** 12 points
147	- **Fill color:** Stone 100 (#F5F5F4) in light mode; Night Stone 100 (#2D2B3A) in dark mode
148	- **Border:** None at rest; on focus, a 2-point Lavender Bloom border appears with smooth 200ms transition
149	- **Label behavior:** Floating label that rises above the field on focus or when content is present; label color transitions from Stone 400 (#A8A29E) to Lavender Bloom on focus
150	- **Error state:** Border becomes Soft Coral (#EF4444), error message appears below in Soft Coral, 14pt
151	- **Minimum height:** 56 points to ensure comfortable touch interaction
152	
153	### Chip
154	- **Shape:** Fully rounded pill (corner radius = half the chip height)
155	- **Corner radius:** 16 points (pill shape)
156	- **Background (default):** Stone 100 (#F5F5F4) in light mode; Night Stone 100 (#2D2B3A) in dark mode
157	- **Background (selected):** Lavender Bloom at 15% opacity (#7C3AED1A), with Lavender Bloom text
158	- **Minimum height:** 32 points (comfortable touch target)
159	- **Horizontal padding:** 12 points left and right
160	- **Tap feedback:** 150ms opacity shift to selected state, no scale change (chips feel like gentle toggles, not buttons)
161	
162	### Bottom Sheet
163	- **Top corner radius:** 28 points — large, prominent rounding that feels organic and soft
164	- **Background:** Warm White (#FFFFFF) in light mode; Charcoal Surface (#252336) in dark mode
165	- **Handle bar:** 40 points wide, 4 points tall, centered at top, Stone 300 (#D6D3D1) color in light mode; Night Stone 200 in dark mode. The handle feels like a gentle grip point, not structural.
166	- **Maximum height:** 90% of screen height for full sheets; 50% for half sheets
167	- **Shadow:** Soft diffused shadow, 16 points blur, 4 points offset-y
168	- **Open animation:** 250ms smooth deceleration — slides up from bottom edge with subtle fade
169	
170	### Navigation Bar (Bottom Tabs)
171	- **Background color:** Warm White (#FFFFFF) in light mode; Charcoal Surface (#252336) in dark mode
172	- **Active indicator:** A small rounded pill beneath the active tab icon and label. The pill is filled with Lavender Bloom at 15% opacity. The indicator transitions smoothly (200ms) between tabs.
173	- **Icon style:** Outlined icons for inactive state, filled icons for active state — the active tab is visually "filled" with color
174	- **Icon size:** 24 points
175	- **Label visibility:** Labels are always visible below icons — no hidden label behavior. Text is SemiBold 11pt when active, Regular 11pt when inactive.
176	- **Touch target:** Each tab item has a minimum 48-point touch target height
177	- **Safe area:** Bottom navigation respects the home indicator area on notched devices
178	
179	### App Bar
180	- **Background:** Transparent to scaffold background color (Lavender Tint #F5F3FF in light mode; Night Sky #13111C in dark mode). The AppBar feels like it floats over the content.
181	- **Title text style:** SemiBold 20pt, Deep Graphite (#1F2937) in light mode; Soft Pearl (#F3F4F6) in dark mode
182	- **Scroll behavior:** On scrollable content, the AppBar has a subtle fade-in effect as content scrolls beneath it. On screens with SliverAppBar, the AppBar collapses to show a smaller representation.
183	- **Leading/back button:** Icon button with 48-point touch target, Lavender Bloom on tap
184	
185	---
186	
187	## 5. Layout Principles
188	
189	- **Base spacing unit:** 8 points — all spacing is derived from multiples of 8
190	- **Screen horizontal padding:** 16 points from each edge
191	- **Section vertical spacing:** 24 points between major sections
192	- **Card internal padding:** 16 points all sides
193	- **Card gap:** 12 points between cards in a grid or list
194	- **List item minimum height:** 56 points (comfortable touch target for interactive list items)
195	- **Minimum touch target:** 48 points (compliant with mobile accessibility standards)
196	- **Bottom sheet handle bar:** 40 points wide, 4 points tall, centered 20 points from top
197	- **Safe area awareness:** Respect status bar at top (add 12 points padding when status bar is visible) and home indicator at bottom (bottom navigation and FAB account for this)
198	- **Grid gutters:** 12 points between columns in 2-column grids
199	- **Card corner radius:** 16 points for standard cards; 12 points for smaller card variants
200	
201	---
202	
203	## 6. Motion & Animation
204	
205	Motion is gentle, purposeful, and never jarring. The app feels like a calm, flowing experience rather than a reactive, mechanical one.
206	
207	- **Page transitions:** 300ms duration, smooth deceleration. Screen content slides and fades simultaneously — the new screen appears to gently settle into place.
208	- **Micro-interactions:** 200ms duration, snappy ease-out. Button presses, chip selections, toggle switches — responses feel quick but soft, like a gentle tap on a responsive surface.
209	- **Hero transitions:** 350ms duration, fast-out-slow-in easing. When navigating from a list to a detail view (e.g., article reader), shared elements like images and titles smoothly expand and continue their motion arc.
210	- **Staggered list reveals:** 50ms delay between each item. When content loads, list items cascade into view in a waterfall — items appear 50ms apart, creating a sense of gentle unfolding rather than a sudden dump of content.
211	- **Bottom sheets:** 250ms duration, smooth deceleration. Sheets slide up from the bottom edge, decelerating naturally as they reach their resting position.
212	- **Pull-to-refresh:** 150ms duration, quick snap. The refresh indicator appears and dismisses quickly but not abruptly.
213	- **Tab indicator movement:** 200ms duration, ease-in-out. The active indicator pill smoothly glides between tab positions.
214	- **Card tap feedback:** 200ms ease-out scale to 98%, then 200ms ease-out return to 100%.
215	- **FAB appearance:** 200ms fade-in with subtle scale from 95% to 100%.
216	
217	---
218	
219	## 7. Anti-Patterns (Banned Design Rules)
220	
221	- No default platform colors — every color comes from the design system palette
222	- No ad-hoc text sizing — all text uses the defined type scale
223	- No inconsistent spacing — all spacing uses the 8-point base unit scale
224	- No arbitrary elevation — every shadow level communicates a specific hierarchy
225	- No Inter or Roboto — Nunito is the only font family
226	- No purple or neon AI aesthetic — colors are warm pastels, not synthetic
227	- No generic gradients — backgrounds are flat or subtly tinted, not gradient-washed
228	- No shadows without purpose — elevation always communicates hierarchy
229	- No desktop patterns — no sidebars, hover tooltips, right-click menus, or desktop-only interaction patterns
230	- No touch targets smaller than 48 points
231	- No critical actions outside the thumb zone (bottom two-thirds of screen height)
232	- No pure black (#000000) anywhere — deep charcoal and off-black only
233	- No pure white (#FFFFFF) for text — use off-white tones that reduce eye strain
[2026-05-19T02:16:32.399Z] [STDOUT] {"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_function_lvi36bsipv0v_1","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Article Reader — Screen Specification\n2\t\n3\t## 1. Screen Title\n4\t**Article Reader**\n5\t\n6\t## 2. Purpose\n7\tDisplay a single article in a clean, readable format with bookmark capability and related article navigation. This is the dedicated reading experience — optimized for extended reading with proper typography, clear hierarchy, and quick access to related content.\n8\t\n9\t## 3. Route\n10\t```\n11\t/article-reader/:id\n12\t```\n13\t- Path parameter `id` identifies the article to display\n14\t- Source screen: Education (`/education`), Home wellness tip\n15\t\n16\t## 4. Widget Name\n17\t`ArticleReaderScreen`\n18\t\n19\t## 5. Design Tokens\n20\t\n21\t### Color Palette (from DESIGN.md)\n22\t| Token | Light Mode | Dark Mode | Usage |\n23\t|---|---|---|---|\n24\t| Primary | `#7C3AED` Lavender Bloom | `#9F67FF` Twilight Bloom | AppBar actions, links |\n25\t| Secondary | `#F9A8D4` Blush Rose | `#FBC4E0` Dusky Rose | Topic badge accent |\n26\t| Surface | `#FAFAFA` Morning Mist | `#1E1B2E` Deep Twilight | Card backgrounds |\n27\t| Scaffold BG | `#F5F3FF` Lavender Tint | `#13111C` Night Sky | Screen background |\n28\t| Body Text | `#1F2937` Deep Graphite | `#F3F4F6` Soft Pearl | Primary text |\n29\t| Secondary Text | `#6B7280` Stone Grey | `#9CA3AF` Muted Silver | Captions, metadata |\n30\t| Divider | `#E5E7EB` Misty Border | `#2D2B3A` Deep Border | Section separators |\n31\t| Error | `#EF4444` Soft Coral | `#F87171` Muted Coral | Validation errors |\n32\t\n33\t### Typography (Nunito — from DESIGN.md)\n34\t| Role | Size | Weight | Line Height | Usage |\n35\t|---|---|---|---|---|\n36\t| Display | 57pt | 700 | 64pt | — |\n37\t| Screen Title | 28pt | 600 | 36pt | AppBar title |\n38\t| Section Header | 22pt | 600 | 28pt | Article title |\n39\t| Subtitle | 16pt | 500 | 24pt | Author, date |\n40\t| Body | 16pt | 400 | 24pt | Article body text |\n41\t| Body Small | 14pt | 400 | 20pt | Captions, metadata |\n42\t| Button Label | 14pt | 600 | 20pt | Chips, labels |\n43\t| Caption | 11pt | 500 | 16pt | Badges, timestamps |\n44\t\n45\t### Spacing (8pt base — from DESIGN.md)\n46\t| Token | Value | Usage |\n47\t|---|---|---|\n48\t| `xxs` | 4dp | Tight internal spacing |\n49\t| `xs` | 8dp | Icon gaps, small padding |\n50\t| `sm` | 12dp | Chip padding |\n51\t| `md` | 16dp | Card padding, section margins |\n52\t| `lg` | 24dp | Section vertical spacing |\n53\t| `xl` | 32dp | Large gaps |\n54\t| `xxl` | 48dp | Screen top/bottom padding |\n55\t\n56\t### Corner Radius\n57\t| Token | Value | Usage |\n58\t|---|---|---|\n59\t| `sm` | 8dp | Chips, small elements |\n60\t| `md` | 12dp | Text fields, bottom sheets |\n61\t| `lg` | 16dp | Cards, large containers |\n62\t| `full` | 999dp | Pills, avatars |\n63\t\n64\t### Motion (from DESIGN.md)\n65\t| Token | Value | Usage |\n66\t|---|---|---|\n67\t| Page transition | 300ms, smooth deceleration | Screen push/pop |\n68\t| Micro-interaction | 200ms, snappy ease-out | Tap feedback, icon toggle |\n69\t| Hero transition | 350ms, fast-out-slow-in | Shared element from article card |\n70\t| Card tap | 200ms scale to 98% | Press feedback |\n71\t\n72\t## 6. Layout Rules\n73\t\n74\t### Scaffold Structure\n75\t```\n76\tScaffold\n77\t├── AppBar (SliverAppBar with collapsing header)\n78\t│   ├── Leading: Back button (48pt touch target)\n79\t│   ├── Title: Article topic text (centered or trailing)\n80\t│   └── Actions: Bookmark icon, Share icon\n81\t├── Body: SingleChildScrollView\n82\t│   ├── SliverAppBar with FlexibleSpace (hero image, collapses on scroll)\n83\t│   └── Remaining content (ArticleHeader, ArticleBody, RelatedArticles)\n84\t└── No BottomNavigationBar, No FAB\n85\t```\n86\t\n87\t### AppBar Behavior\n88\t- Collapsing header: `SliverAppBar` with `flexibleSpace` containing the hero image\n89\t- Background: transparent, blends into scaffold `Lavender Tint`\n90\t- On scroll: image collapses and fades; title transitions from large to compact\n91\t- Back button: standard leading, returns to Education or previous screen\n92\t- Trailing actions: bookmark (toggleable), share (system sheet)\n93\t\n94\t### Navigation Bar\n95\t- Hidden (not visible during article reading)\n96\t- Swipe-back enabled for dismissal\n97\t\n98\t### Screen Padding\n99\t- Horizontal: 16dp from each edge\n100\t- Vertical sections: 24dp between major sections\n101\t- Card internal padding: 16dp\n102\t\n103\t## 7. Sections\n104\t\n105\t### 7.1 Article Header (collapsed view in SliverAppBar)\n106\t\n107\t**Description:** Full-width hero image at top, topic badge, article title, and metadata. When scrolled, this collapses into a compact AppBar representation.\n108\t\n109\t**Widget:** `SliverAppBar` with `flexibleSpace` containing a `Column`\n110\t- Hero image: `BoxFit.cover`, height 240dp expanded / 56dp collapsed\n111\t- Topic badge: `Container` with `Blush Rose` background, white text, pill shape (12dp radius)\n112\t- Title: `Text` with `Section Header` style, max 3 lines, ellipsis overflow\n113\t- Metadata row: Author name, date, estimated read time (separated by `•`)\n114\t\n115\t**Data requirements:**\n116\t```\n117\tArticle {\n118\t  id: String\n119\t  title: String\n120\t  topic: String (e.g., \"Nutrition\", \"Body Changes\")\n121\t  imageUrl: String (hero image URL)\n122\t  authorName: String\n123\t  publishedDate: DateTime\n124\t  readTimeMinutes: int\n125\t}\n126\t```\n127\t\n128\t**Interactive elements:**\n129\t- Hero image: shared element transition (hero) from EducationScreen article card\n130\t- Scroll: collapses header, triggers AppBar fade-in\n131\t\n132\t---\n133\t\n134\t### 7.2 Article Body\n135\t\n136\t**Description:** Formatted text content with section headers and pull-quote styling.\n137\t\n138\t**Widget:** `SingleChildScrollView` → `Padding` → `Column`\n139\t- Section headers: `Text` with `Title Medium` style, `Lavender Bloom` color\n140\t- Body paragraphs: `Text` with `Body` style, `Deep Graphite` color, `0.15` letter spacing\n141\t- Pull quotes: `Container` with `Blush Rose` left border (4dp), italic text, 16dp padding\n142\t- Bullet lists: `Row` with `Blush Rose` dot + body text\n143\t\n144\t**Data requirements:**\n145\t```\n146\tArticle {\n147\t  sections: List<ArticleSection>\n148\t}\n149\t\n150\tArticleSection {\n151\t  type: enum (paragraph, header, pullquote, list)\n152\t  content: String\n153\t  items: List<String>? // for list type\n154\t}\n155\t```\n156\t\n157\t**Interactive elements:**\n158\t- None (read-only content)\n159\t- Links in future: open external browser\n160\t\n161\t---\n162\t\n163\t### 7.3 Related Articles\n164\t\n165\t**Description:** Bottom section displaying 2–3 related article cards in a horizontal `ListView`.\n166\t\n167\t**Widget:** `Column` with section title and horizontal `ListView`\n168\t- Section title: `Text` \"Related Articles\" with `Title Medium` style\n169\t- Related article cards: `InkWell` with `ArticleCard` widget (120dp width, image + title)\n170\t- Card spacing: 12dp between cards\n171\t- Tap → navigate to new `ArticleReaderScreen` with hero transition\n172\t\n173\t**Data requirements:**\n174\t```\n175\tArticle {\n176\t  relatedArticleIds: List<String>\n177\t}\n178\t\n179\tArticleProvider.getArticlesByIds(List<String>) → List<Article>\n180\t```\n181\t\n182\t**Interactive elements:**\n183\t- Tap card: push new `ArticleReaderScreen` with that article's ID\n184\t- Hero transition: article card image and title animate to new screen header\n185\t\n186\t---\n187\t\n188\t### 7.4 Bookmark Action\n189\t\n190\t**Description:** Trailing AppBar icon that toggles article bookmark state.\n191\t\n192\t**Widget:** `IconButton` in AppBar actions\n193\t- Unbookmarked: `Icons.bookmark_outline` (Stone Grey)\n194\t- Bookmarked: `Icons.bookmark` (Lavender Bloom, filled)\n195\t\n196\t**Data requirements:**\n197\t```\n198\tArticle.isBookmarked: bool\n199\tArticleProvider.toggleBookmark(String articleId)\n200\t```\n201\t\n202\t**Interactive elements:**\n203\t- Tap: toggle bookmark state, animate icon with 150ms scale bounce + color transition\n204\t- State persists in `ArticleProvider`\n205\t\n206\t---\n207\t\n208\t### 7.5 Share Action\n209\t\n210\t**Description:** Trailing AppBar icon that opens system share sheet.\n211\t\n212\t**Widget:** `IconButton` in AppBar actions\n213\t- Icon: `Icons.share_outlined` (Stone Grey)\n214\t- Tap → `Share.share(articleUrl, subject: articleTitle)` from `share_plus`\n215\t\n216\t**Data requirements:**\n217\t```\n218\tArticle {\n219\t  shareUrl: String\n220\t  title: String\n221\t}\n222\t```\n223\t\n224\t**Interactive elements:**\n225\t- Tap: open native share sheet with article title and URL\n226\t\n227\t## 8. Data\n228\t\n229\t### Article Entity\n230\t```\n231\tArticle {\n232\t  id: String (unique identifier)\n233\t  title: String (article headline)\n234\t  topic: String (e.g., \"Nutrition\", \"Body Changes\", \"Exercise\", \"Mental Health\")\n235\t  imageUrl: String (hero image URL)\n236\t  authorName: String\n237\t  publishedDate: DateTime\n238\t  readTimeMinutes: int\n239\t  content: List<ArticleSection>\n240\t  relatedArticleIds: List<String>\n241\t  isBookmarked: bool\n242\t  shareUrl: String\n243\t}\n244\t\n245\tArticleSection {\n246\t  type: ArticleSectionType (paragraph, header, pullquote, list)\n247\t  content: String\n248\t  items: List<String>? (for list type)\n249\t}\n250\t```\n251\t\n252\t### Provider: `ArticleProvider`\n253\t- `getArticle(String id)`: returns `Article?`\n254\t- `getRelatedArticles(List<String> ids)`: returns `List<Article>`\n255\t- `toggleBookmark(String id)`: flips `isBookmarked` state\n256\t- State: in-memory for MVP (persisted to local storage in future)\n257\t\n258\t## 9. Motion\n259\t\n260\t### Page Transition\n261\t- Type: push with 300ms slide + fade\n262\t- Curve: `Curves.easeInOut`\n263\t- Back swipe: enabled, reverses the animation\n264\t\n265\t### Hero Transition (from Education Screen)\n266\t- Duration: 350ms\n267\t- Easing: fast-out-slow-in (`Curves.easeOut` enter, `Curves.easeIn` exit)\n268\t- Shared elements: hero image, article title text\n269\t- Trigger: tap article card in EducationScreen → article reader opens\n270\t\n271\t### Header Collapse (SliverAppBar)\n272\t- Behavior: scroll down → header shrinks, image fades\n273\t- Animation: tied to scroll position, continuous\n274\t- Title: transitions from large (22pt) to compact (16pt) as AppBar collapses\n275\t\n276\t### Bookmark Toggle\n277\t- Duration: 150ms\n278\t- Effect: scale 1.0 → 1.2 → 1.0 + color fade from outline to filled\n279\t- Curve: `Curves.easeOut`\n280\t\n281\t### Card Tap (Related Articles)\n282\t- Duration: 200ms\n283\t- Effect: scale to 98% on press, return to 100%\n284\t- Curve: `Curves.easeOut`\n285\t\n286\t## 10. Accessibility\n287\t\n288\t### Semantic Labels\n289\t- Back button: \"Navigate back\"\n290\t- Bookmark icon (unbookmarked): \"Bookmark article\"\n291\t- Bookmark icon (bookmarked): \"Remove bookmark\"\n292\t- Share icon: \"Share article\"\n293\t- Related article card: \"Read [article title]\"\n294\t- Hero image: \"Article hero image\"\n295\t\n296\t### Focus Order\n297\t1. Back button (leading)\n298\t2. Bookmark action\n299\t3. Share action\n300\t4. Article body content (scrollable)\n301\t5. Related article cards (traversed in order)\n302\t\n303\t### Contrast Ratios\n304\t- Body text (`#1F2937` on `#FAFAFA`): 14.7:1 ✓ (exceeds 7:1)\n305\t- Secondary text (`#6B7280` on `#FAFAFA`): 4.6:1 ✓ (exceeds 4.5:1)\n306\t- Topic badge (white on `#F9A8D4`): 3.2:1 ✓ (exceeds 3:1)\n307\t- AppBar title (`#1F2937` on `#F5F3FF`): 12.6:1 ✓ (exceeds 7:1)\n308\t\n309\t### Touch Targets\n310\t- All interactive elements: minimum 48dp × 48dp\n311\t- AppBar icons: 48dp touch target via `IconButton`\n312\t- Related article cards: full card is tappable\n313\t\n314\t### Screen Reader\n315\t- Article title announced when screen loads\n316\t- Section headers announced as navigation landmarks\n317\t- Pull quotes read with emphasis\n318\t\n319\t## 11. Anti-Patterns\n320\t\n321\t**Do NOT:**\n322\t- Use `AppBar` with `title` instead of `SliverAppBar` with collapsing header\n323\t- Show `BottomNavigationBar` (hidden for reading focus)\n324\t- Use pure black (`#000000`) or pure white (`#FFFFFF`) for text\n325\t- Apply hard shadows or aggressive elevation\n326\t- Use Inter, Roboto, or non-Nunito fonts\n327\t- Display more than 3 related articles (overwhelming)\n328\t- Use unsourced placeholder images\n329\t- Allow body text smaller than 16sp\n330\t- Use arbitrary spacing not aligned to 8pt grid\n331\t- Trigger animations longer than 400ms (jarring)\n332\t- Use `ListView` for article body (performance on long articles)"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"92c85158-35a7-431a-be08-06a1045e3fef","uuid":"b3e92174-deb5-4f59-abd1-01cac403daf7","timestamp":"2026-05-19T02:16:32.398Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.stitch/designs/article-reader/SPEC.md","content":"# Article Reader — Screen Specification\n\n## 1. Screen Title\n**Article Reader**\n\n## 2. Purpose\nDisplay a single article in a clean, readable format with bookmark capability and related article navigation. This is the dedicated reading experience — optimized for extended reading with proper typography, clear hierarchy, and quick access to related content.\n\n## 3. Route\n```\n/article-reader/:id\n```\n- Path parameter `id` identifies the article to display\n- Source screen: Education (`/education`), Home wellness tip\n\n## 4. Widget Name\n`ArticleReaderScreen`\n\n## 5. Design Tokens\n\n### Color Palette (from DESIGN.md)\n| Token | Light Mode | Dark Mode | Usage |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Primary | `#7C3AED` Lavender Bloom | `#9F67FF` Twilight Bloom | AppBar actions, links |\n| Secondary | `#F9A8D4` Blush Rose | `#FBC4E0` Dusky Rose | Topic badge accent |\n| Surface | `#FAFAFA` Morning Mist | `#1E1B2E` Deep Twilight | Card backgrounds |\n| Scaffold BG | `#F5F3FF` Lavender Tint | `#13111C` Night Sky | Screen background |\n| Body Text | `#1F2937` Deep Graphite | `#F3F4F6` Soft Pearl | Primary text |\n| Secondary Text | `#6B7280` Stone Grey | `#9CA3AF` Muted Silver | Captions, metadata |\n| Divider | `#E5E7EB` Misty Border | `#2D2B3A` Deep Border | Section separators |\n| Error | `#EF4444` Soft Coral | `#F87171` Muted Coral | Validation errors |\n\n### Typography (Nunito — from DESIGN.md)\n| Role | Size | Weight | Line Height | Usage |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| Display | 57pt | 700 | 64pt | — |\n| Screen Title | 28pt | 600 | 36pt | AppBar title |\n| Section Header | 22pt | 600 | 28pt | Article title |\n| Subtitle | 16pt | 500 | 24pt | Author, date |\n| Body | 16pt | 400 | 24pt | Article body text |\n| Body Small | 14pt | 400 | 20pt | Captions, metadata |\n| Button Label | 14pt | 600 | 20pt | Chips, labels |\n| Caption | 11pt | 500 | 16pt | Badges, timestamps |\n\n### Spacing (8pt base — from DESIGN.md)\n| Token | Value | Usage |\n|---|---|---|\n| `xxs` | 4dp | Tight internal spacing |\n| `xs` | 8dp | Icon gaps, small padding |\n| `sm` | 12dp | Chip padding |\n| `md` | 16dp | Card padding, section margins |\n| `lg` | 24dp | Section vertical spacing |\n| `xl` | 32dp | Large gaps |\n| `xxl` | 48dp | Screen top/bottom padding |\n\n### Corner Radius\n| Token | Value | Usage |\n|---|---|---|\n| `sm` | 8dp | Chips, small elements |\n| `md` | 12dp | Text fields, bottom sheets |\n| `lg` | 16dp | Cards, large containers |\n| `full` | 999dp | Pills, avatars |\n\n### Motion (from DESIGN.md)\n| Token | Value | Usage |\n|---|---|---|\n| Page transition | 300ms, smooth deceleration | Screen push/pop |\n| Micro-interaction | 200ms, snappy ease-out | Tap feedback, icon toggle |\n| Hero transition | 350ms, fast-out-slow-in | Shared element from article card |\n| Card tap | 200ms scale to 98% | Press feedback |\n\n## 6. Layout Rules\n\n### Scaffold Structure\n```\nScaffold\n├── AppBar (SliverAppBar with collapsing header)\n│   ├── Leading: Back button (48pt touch target)\n│   ├── Title: Article topic text (centered or trailing)\n│   └── Actions: Bookmark icon, Share icon\n├── Body: SingleChildScrollView\n│   ├── SliverAppBar with FlexibleSpace (hero image, collapses on scroll)\n│   └── Remaining content (ArticleHeader, ArticleBody, RelatedArticles)\n└── No BottomNavigationBar, No FAB\n```\n\n### AppBar Behavior\n- Collapsing header: `SliverAppBar` with `flexibleSpace` containing the hero image\n- Background: transparent, blends into scaffold `Lavender Tint`\n- On scroll: image collapses and fades; title transitions from large to compact\n- Back button: standard leading, returns to Education or previous screen\n- Trailing actions: bookmark (toggleable), share (system sheet)\n\n### Navigation Bar\n- Hidden (not visible during article reading)\n- Swipe-back enabled for dismissal\n\n### Screen Padding\n- Horizontal: 16dp from each edge\n- Vertical sections: 24dp between major sections\n- Card internal padding: 16dp\n\n## 7. Sections\n\n### 7.1 Article Header (collapsed view in SliverAppBar)\n\n**Description:** Full-width hero image at top, topic badge, article title, and metadata. When scrolled, this collapses into a compact AppBar representation.\n\n**Widget:** `SliverAppBar` with `flexibleSpace` containing a `Column`\n- Hero image: `BoxFit.cover`, height 240dp expanded / 56dp collapsed\n- Topic badge: `Container` with `Blush Rose` background, white text, pill shape (12dp radius)\n- Title: `Text` with `Section Header` style, max 3 lines, ellipsis overflow\n- Metadata row: Author name, date, estimated read time (separated by `•`)\n\n**Data requirements:**\n```\nArticle {\n  id: String\n  title: String\n  topic: String (e.g., \"Nutrition\", \"Body Changes\")\n  imageUrl: String (hero image URL)\n  authorName: String\n  publishedDate: DateTime\n  readTimeMinutes: int\n}\n```\n\n**Interactive elements:**\n- Hero image: shared element transition (hero) from EducationScreen article card\n- Scroll: collapses header, triggers AppBar fade-in\n\n---\n\n### 7.2 Article Body\n\n**Description:** Formatted text content with section headers and pull-quote styling.\n\n**Widget:** `SingleChildScrollView` → `Padding` → `Column`\n- Section headers: `Text` with `Title Medium` style, `Lavender Bloom` color\n- Body paragraphs: `Text` with `Body` style, `Deep Graphite` color, `0.15` letter spacing\n- Pull quotes: `Container` with `Blush Rose` left border (4dp), italic text, 16dp padding\n- Bullet lists: `Row` with `Blush Rose` dot + body text\n\n**Data requirements:**\n```\nArticle {\n  sections: List<ArticleSection>\n}\n\nArticleSection {\n  type: enum (paragraph, header, pullquote, list)\n  content: String\n  items: List<String>? // for list type\n}\n```\n\n**Interactive elements:**\n- None (read-only content)\n- Links in future: open external browser\n\n---\n\n### 7.3 Related Articles\n\n**Description:** Bottom section displaying 2–3 related article cards in a horizontal `ListView`.\n\n**Widget:** `Column` with section title and horizontal `ListView`\n- Section title: `Text` \"Related Articles\" with `Title Medium` style\n- Related article cards: `InkWell` with `ArticleCard` widget (120dp width, image + title)\n- Card spacing: 12dp between cards\n- Tap → navigate to new `ArticleReaderScreen` with hero transition\n\n**Data requirements:**\n```\nArticle {\n  relatedArticleIds: List<String>\n}\n\nArticleProvider.getArticlesByIds(List<String>) → List<Article>\n```\n\n**Interactive elements:**\n- Tap card: push new `ArticleReaderScreen` with that article's ID\n- Hero transition: article card image and title animate to new screen header\n\n---\n\n### 7.4 Bookmark Action\n\n**Description:** Trailing AppBar icon that toggles article bookmark state.\n\n**Widget:** `IconButton` in AppBar actions\n- Unbookmarked: `Icons.bookmark_outline` (Stone Grey)\n- Bookmarked: `Icons.bookmark` (Lavender Bloom, filled)\n\n**Data requirements:**\n```\nArticle.isBookmarked: bool\nArticleProvider.toggleBookmark(String articleId)\n```\n\n**Interactive elements:**\n- Tap: toggle bookmark state, animate icon with 150ms scale bounce + color transition\n- State persists in `ArticleProvider`\n\n---\n\n### 7.5 Share Action\n\n**Description:** Trailing AppBar icon that opens system share sheet.\n\n**Widget:** `IconButton` in AppBar actions\n- Icon: `Icons.share_outlined` (Stone Grey)\n- Tap → `Share.share(articleUrl, subject: articleTitle)` from `share_plus`\n\n**Data requirements:**\n```\nArticle {\n  shareUrl: String\n  title: String\n}\n```\n\n**Interactive elements:**\n- Tap: open native share sheet with article title and URL\n\n## 8. Data\n\n### Article Entity\n```\nArticle {\n  id: String (unique identifier)\n  title: String (article headline)\n  topic: String (e.g., \"Nutrition\", \"Body Changes\", \"Exercise\", \"Mental Health\")\n  imageUrl: String (hero image URL)\n  authorName: String\n  publishedDate: DateTime\n  readTimeMinutes: int\n  content: List<ArticleSection>\n  relatedArticleIds: List<String>\n  isBookmarked: bool\n  shareUrl: String\n}\n\nArticleSection {\n  type: ArticleSectionType (paragraph, header, pullquote, list)\n  content: String\n  items: List<String>? (for list type)\n}\n```\n\n### Provider: `ArticleProvider`\n- `getArticle(String id)`: returns `Article?`\n- `getRelatedArticles(List<String> ids)`: returns `List<Article>`\n- `toggleBookmark(String id)`: flips `isBookmarked` state\n- State: in-memory for MVP (persisted to local storage in future)\n\n## 9. Motion\n\n### Page Transition\n- Type: push with 300ms slide + fade\n- Curve: `Curves.easeInOut`\n- Back swipe: enabled, reverses the animation\n\n### Hero Transition (from Education Screen)\n- Duration: 350ms\n- Easing: fast-out-slow-in (`Curves.easeOut` enter, `Curves.easeIn` exit)\n- Shared elements: hero image, article title text\n- Trigger: tap article card in EducationScreen → article reader opens\n\n### Header Collapse (SliverAppBar)\n- Behavior: scroll down → header shrinks, image fades\n- Animation: tied to scroll position, continuous\n- Title: transitions from large (22pt) to compact (16pt) as AppBar collapses\n\n### Bookmark Toggle\n- Duration: 150ms\n- Effect: scale 1.0 → 1.2 → 1.0 + color fade from outline to filled\n- Curve: `Curves.easeOut`\n\n### Card Tap (Related Articles)\n- Duration: 200ms\n- Effect: scale to 98% on press, return to 100%\n- Curve: `Curves.easeOut`\n\n## 10. Accessibility\n\n### Semantic Labels\n- Back button: \"Navigate back\"\n- Bookmark icon (unbookmarked): \"Bookmark article\"\n- Bookmark icon (bookmarked): \"Remove bookmark\"\n- Share icon: \"Share article\"\n- Related article card: \"Read [article title]\"\n- Hero image: \"Article hero image\"\n\n### Focus Order\n1. Back button (leading)\n2. Bookmark action\n3. Share action\n4. Article body content (scrollable)\n5. Related article cards (traversed in order)\n\n### Contrast Ratios\n- Body text (`#1F2937` on `#FAFAFA`): 14.7:1 ✓ (exceeds 7:1)\n- Secondary text (`#6B7280` on `#FAFAFA`): 4.6:1 ✓ (exceeds 4.5:1)\n- Topic badge (white on `#F9A8D4`): 3.2:1 ✓ (exceeds 3:1)\n- AppBar title (`#1F2937` on `#F5F3FF`): 12.6:1 ✓ (exceeds 7:1)\n\n### Touch Targets\n- All interactive elements: minimum 48dp × 48dp\n- AppBar icons: 48dp touch target via `IconButton`\n- Related article cards: full card is tappable\n\n### Screen Reader\n- Article title announced when screen loads\n- Section headers announced as navigation landmarks\n- Pull quotes read with emphasis\n\n## 11. Anti-Patterns\n\n**Do NOT:**\n- Use `AppBar` with `title` instead of `SliverAppBar` with collapsing header\n- Show `BottomNavigationBar` (hidden for reading focus)\n- Use pure black (`#000000`) or pure white (`#FFFFFF`) for text\n- Apply hard shadows or aggressive elevation\n- Use Inter, Roboto, or non-Nunito fonts\n- Display more than 3 related articles (overwhelming)\n- Use unsourced placeholder images\n- Allow body text smaller than 16sp\n- Use arbitrary spacing not aligned to 8pt grid\n- Trigger animations longer than 400ms (jarring)\n- Use `ListView` for article body (performance on long articles)","numLines":332,"startLine":1,"totalLines":332}}}
