123	## Complete `data-flutter` Reference
124	
125	| Value | Flutter Widget | Extra Attributes |
126	|-------|---------------|------------------|
127	| `scaffold` | `Scaffold()` | — |
128	| `app-bar` | `AppBar()` | — |
129	| `bottom-nav` | `NavigationBar()` | — |
130	| `nav-destination` | `NavigationDestination()` | `data-icon`, `data-label`, `data-selected` |
131	| `fab` | `FloatingActionButton()` | `data-icon` |
132	| `hero` | `Hero()` | `data-tag` |
133	| `cached-image` | `CachedNetworkImage()` | — |
134	| `sliver-app-bar` | `SliverAppBar()` | `data-expanded-height`, `data-pinned` |
135	| `custom-scroll` | `CustomScrollView()` | — |
136	| `sliver-list` | `SliverList()` | — |
137	| `sliver-grid` | `SliverGrid()` | `data-columns` |
138	| `tab-bar` | `TabBar()` | — |
139	| `tab-view` | `TabBarView()` | — |
140	| `bottom-sheet` | `showModalBottomSheet()` | — |
141	| `dialog` | `showDialog()` / `AlertDialog` | — |
142	| `safe-area` | `SafeArea()` | — |
143	| `refresh` | `RefreshIndicator()` | — |
144	
145	---
146	
147	## Rules
148	
149	1. **Tailwind does ALL styling** — colors, spacing, typography, borders, shadows, layout
150	2. **`data-flutter` only for identity** — which Flutter widget, not how it looks
151	3. **`data-flutter` is optional** — most elements inferred from HTML + Tailwind (`div.flex.flex-col` → Column)
152	4. **Icons** — inline SVG with comment: `<!-- home -->`, `<!-- arrow_back -->`
153	5. **Converter reads** Tailwind classes + `data-flutter` + HTML structure — CSS is ignored
